    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p>Mail</p>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>New Orleans</placeName>
                <date>May 18th</date>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(12)">
                <date>1857</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">I received your<lb/> favor of <date>28<hi rend="sup">th</hi></date>
                Ult. addressed to me<lb/> in my official capacity. Your numerous<lb/> friends here
                are rejoiced to learn of your<lb/> resumption of ministerial duties, which<lb/> they
                regard as cause for congratulation<lb/> to yourself as well as the Israelites<lb/>
                of <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>. It is not in the<lb/> power of our
                congregation to aid you<lb/> as proposed—<hi rend="underline">it has no surplus
                    funds</hi>.<lb/> In order to complete the new Synagogue<lb/> &amp; buildings
                adjacent a mortgage had<lb/> to be given upon its <hi rend="underline">last</hi>
                other property<lb/> so that we are in debt with but a<lb/> limited revenue, our
                    pay<hi rend="underline">in</hi>g members<lb/> not exceeding 45. The “Widow &amp;
                Orphans<lb/> Home” in which all here feel a just<lb/> pride has an insufficient
                revenue<lb/> and demands from <hi rend="underline">all</hi> our people</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>all the public or private surplus funds<lb/> at command. Our city unlike
                    <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName><lb/> has among our people few wealthy
                persons,<lb/> and the few have such constant calls<lb/> at home, that they are
                unable to lend<lb/> or give abroad. With <sic>with</sic> my<lb/> warmest regards I
                am</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">Yours Very Respy</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)"><persName role="author">Geo Jonas</persName> President</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">Congregation “Dispersed of Judah”</p>
        </body>
    </text>
